## Session 3: Technical Updates

### Task 3.1: Add BRIN Index (Section 19)

**Location:** Database schema section

**Content:**
```sql
-- BRIN index for time-series mileage data
-- 128x smaller than B-tree, optimal for append-only tables
CREATE INDEX idx_mileage_history_brin ON mileage_history
  USING BRIN (recorded_at) WITH (pages_per_range = 128);

-- Partial index for recent data (last 90 days)
CREATE INDEX idx_mileage_recent ON mileage_history (train_id, recorded_at DESC)
  WHERE recorded_at > NOW() - INTERVAL '90 days';
```

